title: Genome Sequences of Rhinovirus Genotype C56 Detected in Three Patients with Acute Respiratory Illness, California, 2016 to 2017
body: The genome sequences of RV-C56 strains USA/2016/CA-RGDS-1002 and USA/2017/CA-RGDS-1003 have been deposited in GenBank under the accession numbers MG950178 and MG950179, respectively.
